co.cask.coopr.store.credential

Class InProcessCredentialStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractIdleService
      • co.cask.coopr.store.credential.InProcessCredentialStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CredentialStore, com.google.common.util.concurrent.Service

    public class InProcessCredentialStore
extends com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractIdleService
implements CredentialStore
    Credential store that stores sensitive data in memory in the server process. Only viable if there is a single server, as data will not be available across multiple servers.
